comments: Hollis-Jefferson (POR) makes contact with George's (LAC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) slightly extends his arm into Batum's (POR) body, but does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Little (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of George (LAC), firms up, and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Jackson (LAC) makes marginal contact with Anthony's (POR) leg and does not affect his SQBR.
Little (POR) makes marginal contact to Zubac's (LAC) body during his shooting motion on his shot attempt near the rim.
Hollis-Jefferson (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Batum (LAC) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Hollis-Jefferson (POR) collapses his arm and absorbs the contact to George's (LAC) body during his driving shot attempt.
Little (POR) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and any contact with George's (LAC) arm is marginal.
George (LAC) drives to the basket and marginal contact occurs with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his SQBR.
